{"lastModified":1748869417010,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nAn Inviting and Secure Sailboat\n\nTo experience the comfort, aesthetic design, and spaciousness of the Sun Odyssey 410, you might almost forget you are aboard a high-performance sailboat, where innovations have been made, above all, to improve cruising efficiency, effectiveness, and security. Recessed sidedecks, raised coaming, the lowered boom, and the inverted bow have all been designed in this spirit, while also contributing to the elegance and style of this sail-boat.\n\nErgonomic Design for Well-Being on Board\n\nThe cockpit is secure and comfortable while cruising and transforms easily into an exterior saloon or sundeck while at anchor. The gentle, three-step companionway to the saloon contributes to the feeling of unified space between the interior and exterior. The warm, inviting interior saloon is bathed in light, while the vast cockpit saloon, dedicated to well-being, encourages interaction and shared moments on the exterior. Bright, spacious cabins enable you to savour moments of privacy and rest. Each living space contributes to an enjoyable, harmonious life on board, whether for weekends with friends or longer expeditions.","blueprint":{"name":"NASTAZIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347::assets::c40c1800-3af9-11f0-8ca9-b7c2e68d0b9d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347::assets::c40efe30-3af9-11f0-81c1-69a52c12c739/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347::assets::c40a6a50-3af9-11f0-8ca8-b7c2e68d0b9d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347::assets::c40a9160-3af9-11f0-8ca8-b7c2e68d0b9d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5a64bd50-3af7-11f0-bb0b-2baa0af83347::assets::c40a9161-3af9-11f0-8ca8-b7c2e68d0